            </table><br clear="all" /><div id="title"><span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:0.9em;"> An act to amend the Budget Act of 2024 (Chs. 22, 35, and 994, Stats. 2024), by amending Sections 5.25 and 39.10 of that act,
                  relating to the state budget, and making an appropriation therefor, to take effect immediately, budget bill. </span></div><br clear="all" /><div align="center">
               									
               [									<span style="  font-size: 1.3em">
